{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Joltt \u2013 Battle Pillars is a new kind of 2D fighting game where wizards duel in magical jousts. Victory isn\u2019t about depleting your opponent\u2019s health, but making them fall from their pillar. Outmaneuver their attacks and knock them off with your magical projectiles to be the last one standing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3353130/extras/PvsL03d2.gif?t=1736255417\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There is no blocking in Joltt.\u00a0Read your opponent\u2019s mind, dodge, evade and counter everything to be victorious!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Learn and master 6 different wizards, each having a vastly different gameplay!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ell uses powerful feints and casts multiple projectiles.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Alsnad has great control over the speed of his projectiles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Xioko uses the power of the wind and can fly freely.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Braboz summons unpredictable portals and can teleport around the battlefield.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Myra has access to different mode by igniting her sword with coloured flames.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Okhpum has to summon spirits to gain access to his most powerful moves.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3353130/extras/battle04.gif?t=1736255417\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Be the first one to fill up your super bar and unleash your devastating super move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No complicated inputs. No execution required. All powers are cast with a simple button press, sometimes associated with a direction. You\u2019ll go straight into the mind